  "id": "RAW_2dc03364",
  "title": "AI 办公硬件新标杆：未来智能携 viaim 亮相 CES 2026，斩获微软人工智能创新奖",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247653463&idx=2&sn=b668d5a56de8ff72350270732e861749",
  "date": "2026-01-09 03:35:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"327\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqpHia7H86iawx8XePGDc7reKS7p2HicUtNeUo8lbcLSpHlcCME0tAusu9rg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"7008\" data-cropy2=\"3964.733564013841\" data-imgfileid=\"100169740\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0bfdc3cf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqp3c7e99HWaDrwaaIEKv82RGQkrTIAP0tB8JxohPsGXyXm1nR3qUkFHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | 刘双</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1 月 6 日至 9 日，全球消费电子领域的顶级盛会 CES 2026（国际消费电子展）在拉斯维加斯正式启幕。作为全球科技产业的“风向标”，本届 CES 吸引了 4112 家企业参展，从芯片到硬件再到垂直场景应用，上千家企业同台展示 AI 的深度融合及应用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100169723\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"1\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100169724\" data-ratio=\"0.5595895816890292\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1267\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=598983d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqpYu38yictBevcCPrlKKUHyeSuibY7J1e38ltlmrZgETVkich1djBXkZYLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">中国 AI 硬件明星企业「未来智能」也携旗下全球化品牌 viaim 再度参展，以“We aim to explore”为主题的展台，凭借科技感十足的设计与沉浸式场景体验，成为展会焦点。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">CES 现场，未来智能不仅带来了讯飞 AI 会议耳机 Pro3 与 Air2，更斩获微软颁发的“人工智能创新奖（MICROSOFT AI INNOVATION AWARD）”，展现出中国 AI 硬件品牌的全球竞争力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;font-weight: 500;color: #4285f4;\"><span leaf=\"\">精准定义场景，AI 耳机为全球办公“解题”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在黑、白、橙三色交织的 viaim 展台，讯飞 AI 会议耳机 Pro3 与 Air2 两款产品正吸引着大量观众驻足体验，他们佩戴着耳机，亲身体验着 AI 如何将语音实时转化为结构化的文字、跨语言的知识与可执行的待办事项。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100169728\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1269\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3ca6bd6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqp6CmPbktjxDkppYgoZnzxXfYFEXVYQyCPYqVSTs3ibJJKPh1j8WZHAPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">两款耳机均以“AI work mate”为定位，深度融合 AI 技术与个人办公需求，形成从语音捕捉、信息处理到智能交互的全链路解决方案。相较于市场上普通的 AI 耳机，其不仅覆盖了录音转写、实时翻译、摘要待办提取等基础功能，更创新实现了 AI 嘴替、脑图生成、深度问询及职业定制化摘要等进阶能力，配合最新升级的“你好，小万”语音唤醒功能，无需手动操作即可实时响应，实现对办公全场景的智能伴随与赋能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100169729\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb587d0a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqpem6dVxwA7b6UFUiarnMgAfJLHNc5KnRqQw77areYnFQUDNGic8zZgyHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">讯飞 AI 会议耳机 Pro3 与 Air2 的核心竞争力，本质上是对办公场景核心痛点的精准洞察与解决。无论海内外，办公场景中的会议记录繁琐、多语言沟通障碍、远程办公即时响应滞后等问题都长期存在，而未来智能的产品功能设计恰好精准命中这些需求——录音转写、AI 摘要和 AI 问答等功能解决了多场景会议的记录、总结与查找痛点，实时翻译能力打破了跨境沟通的语言壁垒，AI 嘴替则适配了远程办公中不便发声的特殊场景。这种以场景痛点为导向的功能设计，让产品不再是单纯的技术堆砌，而是真正服务于办公效率提升的实用工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">不同于市场上侧重娱乐属性的消费级耳机，或是功能单一的办公录音转写设备，未来智能以“办公刚需”为核心，避开了消费级音频设备的红海竞争，通过 AI 技术与办公场景的深度绑定，在 AI 办公硬件赛道中形成了独特的竞争壁垒，这也成为其打动全球市场的关键。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;font-weight: 500;color: #4285f4;\"><span leaf=\"\">全球化布局这一年：海外市场增长势能初显</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">自去年 1 月在 CES 2025 上正式宣布以 viaim 品牌进军全球市场以来，未来智能的出海征程已满一整年。这一年，从北美、亚太，到中东、欧洲，未来智能逐步构建起覆盖全球主要市场的销售网络，市场数据也印证了其出海战略的成功。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100169730\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"1\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100169731\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7886e52c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqpTibbOs27W9duT0iawEXtWnAORqlCaInrGQQaOnbWJoo1JLWq2WXw9IlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">据未来智能披露，2025 年全年，viaim 在北美市场的绝对销量增长超 17 倍，四季度表现尤为亮眼，11 月、12 月的月销量环比增幅分别达 54.2%、99.96%，持续刷新年内销售峰值。在亚太及中东市场，viaim 已覆盖日本、阿联酋、新加坡、马来西亚、泰国等多个国家，从 1 月的高基数开局，到 5 月单月销量暴涨超 35 倍、7 月 GMV 增长超 3 倍，再到 12 月以全年最高销售峰值收官，同样实现了全年的稳步增长。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样的成绩，源于未来智能对海外市场的深度调研与精准适配。未来智能 CEO 马啸透露，未来智能团队通过长期的海外市场调研，精准捕捉到海外办公场景中的智能化硬件市场仍存在明显的供给缺口，尤其是能够整合多语言交互、高效信息处理等复合功能的产品极为稀缺，而这正是中国 AI 硬件企业的关键机会点。基于对这一市场空白的精准判断，未来智能的产品在功能定义阶段就瞄准了全球办公人群的共性需求，形成了差异化的竞争优势，这也是其敢于大举进军海外市场的底气所在。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100169732\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"1\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100169733\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=34cb7d23&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqpCxrbeRVn2LGVcoWVA3633B4PzgeOFDkicdXOic2a47GN3zErXPjyLRVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">值得关注的是，2025 年，未来智能先后完成了三轮融资，资金也重点投向了海外市场的调研深化与渠道拓展，进一步夯实精准适配的基础。马啸称，海外市场的复杂性决定了“产品平移”策略难以奏效，未来智能的核心思路是“本地化创新”，即在保持核心 AI 技术优势的前提下，针对不同市场的用户习惯、办公场景差异进行定制优化，通过深度适配能力挖掘市场增长潜力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">安永发布的《智能电子产品海外市场洞察报告》显示，中国智能电子品牌已步入高端化与本土化出海新阶段，北美市场消费者注重高端化与技术驱动，欧洲市场强调品质与可持续消费，亚太市场则侧重性价比与刚需场景。未来智能的全球化布局恰好契合这一趋势，随着精准的市场定位与本地化策略逐渐落地，未来智能有望在海外市场实现更大突破。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;font-weight: 500;color: #4285f4;\"><span leaf=\"\">构建全场景 AI 办公生态，打造智能工作伙伴</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">CES 展会现场的一大亮点，是微软为未来智能颁发了“人工智能创新奖（MICROSOFT AI INNOVATION AWARD）”，这一来自全球科技巨头的权威奖项，不仅是对未来智能以创新功能解决实际需求的肯定，更清晰印证了未来智能“AI+ 办公硬件”产品路线的正确性。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100169734\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"1\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-retry=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1269\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100169735\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43a77d00&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOlhnk4WpfByIowaW1MFNKqpcX5Wo726NfjIWWaMaLyIcXIhaJfzkwkjWicwNV9mAXWhYiaT6cxguwNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">沿着这一产品路线，未来智能正在以耳机为切入点，逐步构建全场景 AI 办公生态，而这一生态的核心支撑正是未来智能自研的 viaim 大脑——一款面向个人的商务办公 AI 智能体。依托这一核心大脑，未来智能将在现有听觉终端（耳机）的基础上，逐步延伸出融合多维度感官的办公硬件，形成覆盖全办公场景的智能终端矩阵。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些不同维度的硬件终端将承担数据收集的核心功能，把个人办公场景中的各类信息实时传回 viaim 大脑，由大脑完成整理、分析、决策乃至执行的全链路处理，最终实现“AI work mate”的核心目标。与此同时，硬件终端收集的真实办公数据，又将反向喂养 viaim 大脑，使其在持续的交互中不断进化，变得更懂用户需求。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，AI 技术正从算力基础设施向现实世界部署延伸，AI 硬件尤其成为重要落地载体。在本届 CES 聚焦 AI 硬件生态的大背景下，未来智能的“一脑多端”战略不仅符合产业发展趋势，也为 AI 硬件的创新发展提供了新方向。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">从 2025 年在 CES 上官宣全球化品牌 viaim，到 2026 年持续携产品与奖项亮相，CES 这一全球科技盛会见证了未来智能的成长轨迹，也见证了中国 AI 硬件品牌从技术突破到全球化发展的崛起之路。随着海外布局的持续深化与 AI 办公生态的逐步构建，未来智能有望在全球 AI 硬件赛道占据更重要的位置，为全球用户带来更高效、智能的办公体验。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "未来智能携 viaim 品牌在 CES 2026 展会亮相，凭借其专为办公场景设计的 AI 会议耳机系列及“一脑多端”的 AI 办公生态战略，斩获微软人工智能创新奖，并展现了其在海外市场显著的增长态势。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "未来智能携 viaim 品牌在 CES 2026 展会亮相，凭借其专为办公场景设计的 AI 会议耳机系列及“一脑多端”的 AI 办公生态战略，斩获微软人工智能创新奖，并展现了其在海外市场显著的增长态势。",
  "summary": "文章报道了中国 AI 硬件企业未来智能及其全球品牌 viaim 在 CES 2026 上的表现。未来智能展示了讯飞 AI 会议耳机 Pro3 与 Air2，这些产品以“AI work mate”为定位，提供录音转写、实时翻译、AI 摘要、AI 嘴替等高级功能，精准解决了全球办公场景中的痛点，并在消费级设备红海中开辟了 AI 办公硬件这一独特赛道。此外，未来智能凭借其创新产品和“一脑多端”的 AI 办公生态战略，荣获微软人工智能创新奖。文章还详细阐述了 viaim 品牌在北美、亚太、中东等海外市场的显著增长，得益于对本地化需求的深度调研和定制优化策略。未来智能正以耳机为切入点，构建以自研 viaim 大脑为核心的全场景 AI 办公生态，旨在融合多维度感官硬件，实现办公信息的全链路处理和智能反馈，为全球用户带来更高效的智能办公体验。",
